data.title: Eight WHL Players named to Team Canada's National Junior Team
data.meta_description: REGINA, SK — Hockey Canada and the Canadian Hockey League (CHL) announced on Wednesday the 22 players that will make up Canada’s National Junior Team for the upcoming 2010 IIHF World Junior Championship in Saskatchewan, from December 26, 2009 to January 5, 2010. Eight of the 22 players named to the roster are from the…
